(bash) Tj T*
(docker compose up -d postgres) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Apply Stage 0 migrations:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(./scripts/db_migrate.sh) Tj T*
(./scripts/db_status.sh) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The migration runner loads .env when present, creates schema_migrations, and applies SQL) Tj T*
(files from database/migrations in filename order. The first migration enables required) Tj T*
(extensions and creates the Stage 0 model-task logging table.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Required extensions for the first migration:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- pgcrypto) Tj T*
(- uuid-ossp) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Stage 0 tables:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- schema_migrations) Tj T*
(- model_task_logs) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(OLLAMA SETUP) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Ollama must run locally only and the approved V1 local model is qwen3:4b.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Recommended secure defaults:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH"   # only needed for a user-space install) Tj T*
(export OLLAMA_HOST=127.0.0.1:11434) Tj T*
(ollama serve) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(In another terminal, install and validate the approved model:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(bash) Tj T*
(./scripts/install_ollama_qwen3_4b.sh) Tj T*
(./scripts/test_ollama_qwen3_4b.sh) Tj T*
() Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The validation scripts fail if Ollama is unreachable, if qwen3:4b is missing, or if) Tj T*
(unexpected local Ollama models are present.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(PAID MODEL SETUP) Tj T*
ET
